  "instructions": [
    "heat the coconut oil in a tava or griddle over medium heat",
    "add the mustard seeds and let them sizzle for a few seconds",
    "add the turmeric and garam masala and stir for a few seconds",
    "add the chopped red onion and cook until it is translucent",
    "add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute",
    "add the long-grain rice and stir to coat with the spice mixture",
    "add 2 cups of water to the tava and bring to a boil",
    "reduce the heat to low, cover the tava, and cook for 18 minutes",
    "fluff the rice pilaf with a fork and garnish with chopped cilantro and a squeeze of lemon juice"
